is a big responsibility.

523
00:37:08,100 --> 00:37:09,100
I'm sure you'll do well.

524
00:37:09,167 --> 00:37:10,767
Thank you very much.

525
00:37:10,833 --> 00:37:12,800
You want to go out and celebrate?

526
00:37:12,867 --> 00:37:14,600
I guess so.

527
00:37:15,667 --> 00:37:18,400
-Huh?
-You bought such a wonderful dress.

528
00:37:18,467 --> 00:37:19,933
It would be a shame for it to go to waste.

529
00:37:20,833 --> 00:37:22,900
-Well.
-Don't worry, I won't say anything.

530
00:37:22,967 --> 00:37:25,867
Just dress up nice,
and go out with a man.

531
00:37:25,933 --> 00:37:27,767
That will say a lot about you.

532
00:37:27,833 --> 00:37:30,067
No, no.

533
00:37:30,133 --> 00:37:32,667
You don't want to be alone with me.

534
00:37:32,733 --> 00:37:35,000
How about we take him along?

535
00:37:35,567 --> 00:37:36,567
Huh?

536
00:37:36,633 --> 00:37:40,000
No, it's not about
whether or not Sosuke is there.

537
00:37:40,067 --> 00:37:41,800
Why?
It's okay if he's around, right?

538
00:37:44,567 --> 00:37:45,567
What is it?

539
00:37:46,500 --> 00:37:50,767
You completely lack basic female powers.

540
00:37:50,833 --> 00:37:53,333
That's obvious.

541
00:37:54,367 --> 00:37:55,733
What are you looking for?

542
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,300
Naturally, your interest

543
00:37:57,367 --> 00:38:00,267
in clothes and makeup
should be emphasized.

544
00:38:00,333 --> 00:38:03,967
Didn't you ever secretly wear
your mom's lipstick?

545
00:38:04,033 --> 00:38:05,767
I didn't have a mother.

546
00:38:07,167 --> 00:38:10,067
Well, don't worry about that.

547
00:38:10,133 --> 00:38:14,667
I'm perfectly happy with having been
properly raised by my father.

548
00:38:16,100 --> 00:38:17,167
Right, then.

549
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:24,000
You're the one using that machine, right?

550
00:38:26,267 --> 00:38:29,100
I apologize for not asking.

551
00:38:29,167 --> 00:38:31,567
It's the first sewing machine
I ever bought.

552
00:38:33,333 --> 00:38:34,867
I guess it still works.

553
00:38:36,067 --> 00:38:37,233
Yes.

554
00:38:47,667 --> 00:38:49,200
I miss it.

555
00:38:50,367 --> 00:38:53,267
I used to work with that thing
day and night.

556
00:38:55,567 --> 00:38:58,433
I just didn't want to lose to clothes.

557
00:38:59,567 --> 00:39:01,633
But then, I failed.

558
00:39:03,367 --> 00:39:05,567
Actually, I regret it.

559
00:39:09,633 --> 00:39:12,067
That's why I put that machine away.

560
00:39:19,067 --> 00:39:21,233
We've been through so much.

561
00:39:23,133 --> 00:39:24,133
Yes.

562
00:39:26,933 --> 00:39:29,900
Is that what it means?

563
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:31,933
What is?

564
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:34,567
To make something that people can't see.

565
00:39:35,467 --> 00:39:39,200
Like hidden thoughts,
or the desire to fight.

566
00:39:40,500 --> 00:39:41,700
Here?

567
00:39:42,533 --> 00:39:43,733
Pent up in here?

568
00:39:46,567 --> 00:39:48,433
Come on, now.

569
00:39:48,500 --> 00:39:50,500
It's just underwear.

570
00:39:54,733 --> 00:39:55,967
Here.

571
00:39:56,033 --> 00:39:57,467
Huh?

572
00:40:40,967 --> 00:40:42,600
You're beautiful!

573
00:40:42,667 --> 00:40:44,667
You look so different.

574
00:40:44,733 --> 00:40:47,233
Wait, did you get taller?

575
00:40:47,300 --> 00:40:49,700
She's transformed into a goddess.

576
00:40:49,767 --> 00:40:51,433
The boys aren't quite up to par.

577
00:40:51,500 --> 00:40:53,633
Be quiet,
this is a style too.

578
00:40:57,467 --> 00:40:58,600
Shall we go?

579
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:04,267
See you.

580
00:41:08,267 --> 00:41:09,333
I'll see you all later.

581
00:41:18,967 --> 00:41:21,233
All right. Let's go.

582
00:41:21,300 --> 00:41:22,400
Yes.

